multiFit

Author: J. Michael Burgess


About:

General wrapper o pymultinest and MULTINEST. 

Currently, three likelihoods are provided: chi2, cstat, and pgstat.

Much work and more documentation are to come....

email: jamesb@kth.se


INSTALL:


Install MULTINEST and pymultinest



git clone https://github.com/drJfunk/mnfit.git
cd mnfit
python setup.py build
python setup.py install


Dependencies:

MULTINEST (https://github.com/JohannesBuchner/MultiNest)
pymultinest

numpy
cython
scipy


